&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you an inpatient nurse or working in acute environment and would like to experience a day in the community?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We would like to offer you the opportunity to come along and shadow our community nurses for a day. This will give you the chance to see what we do and bust some common misconceptions about community nursing which are:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;De-skilling&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Not a wide range of clinical activity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Worried about feeling isolated&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Losing your ability to manage acutely ill patients&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For more information please contact Hollie Winkworth on 02380 475160.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
